Titolo: Infernal: Hell's Vengeance

Anno: 2009

Descrizione: Infernal: Hell's Vengeance is a third-person shooter published by Playlogic. Infernal: Hell's Vengeance is a port of the 2007 PC game Infernal. It tells the story of Ryan Lennox, a fallen angel recruited by Hell to fight Heaven's own secret agency, known as Etherlight.